Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(把上司妻子用肉棒套子上了)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上就去拿替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這次真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,現在正在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,最近真倒楣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,工作不太順利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定會被部長的太太罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,部長叫我來拿行李
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,行李已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的要反省一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公出差多久呢?\N他說兩三天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也許會需要三四天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是我和老公的結婚紀念日阿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我都去了美容院也做了好多料理,準備了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這下怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這是行李
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,失禮了  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 我是祥子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你還沒吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公叫我留你吃頓飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多剩菜你也有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  他都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼站著  坐下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要喝紅酒  你喝嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,多少喝一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,全都吃完不要剩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我很努力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說最近你犯了很多錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始我老公還對你很期待\N這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法會報你們的期待  很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,向我道歉有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有女朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,女朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不會和女孩交往的男人,也做不好工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老公不知出軌多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果不是這樣,也沒辦法住這樣的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,給我好好學習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,酒沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還要喝嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,基本沒怎麼喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是我們的結婚紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,多喝一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你沒有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,女朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有就是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有喜歡的女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是工作上還沒穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,最近一次做愛是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 總是一個人自慰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是男人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,必須要會這樣玩才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妳幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你最近沒摸過女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快點穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我這樣很害羞嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來今天想和我老公做愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,來摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不能摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是部長的太太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很久沒摸過奶子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣部長會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是有責任的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他去出差了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,更溫柔一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我很為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我都已經這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還害羞嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不太習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要直接看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要摸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子都做不到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你更別想升職了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摸喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你連上司的妻子都不敢上嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快點來摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很軟嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不痛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好軟阿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是手指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還要舔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,做不到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,更多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好大膽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:13:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這都是誰的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼不必呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,說了可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,舔我的奶子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,從後面插入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好負責喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,插入深處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,插入深處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,插入更深吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,更多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,更激烈地插吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,更多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,更多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼快的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要變得奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒滿足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:20:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,自己動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,更多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,多插一些
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.18,0:25:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,多動一些
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.95,0:25:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.48,0:26:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,因為太爽了  真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.77,0:26:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.34,0:26:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.37,0:26:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.84,0:26:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,還要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.95,0:26:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有那麼強大
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.55,0:27:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.32,0:27:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.66,0:27:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.10,0:27:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.13,0:27:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,今天多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.57,0:27:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.24,0:27:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.42,0:27:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.53,0:27:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喝點酒  我自己自慰算了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.60,0:28:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好暈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.47,0:28:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.86,0:28:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  我是祥子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.70,0:28:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我有點事找你  能過來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.04,0:29:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.85,0:29:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.49,0:29:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,把包放下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.32,0:29:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.57,0:30:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為你的錯  我現在好閒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.20,0:30:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.14,0:30:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.36,0:30:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.77,0:30:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.71,0:30:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.98,0:30:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.35,0:31:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你做愛真的好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.33,0:31:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.76,0:31:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要有更多經驗才行\N這樣子沒辦法滿足女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.24,0:31:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.35,0:31:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,做愛要強大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.06,0:31:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩子都希望這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.26,0:32:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,使用這個試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.57,0:32:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有在聽我說嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.51,0:32:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.38,0:32:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.01,0:32:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的事  希望能對我老公保密
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.95,0:32:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.15,0:32:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡嘗試一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.59,0:32:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.93,0:32:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.27,0:32:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再給我一次機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.64,0:33:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.15,0:33:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再給我一次機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.52,0:33:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你想光明正大地玩弄上司的妻子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.25,0:33:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.82,0:33:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.63,0:33:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.76,0:33:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.81,0:33:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天是因為喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.18,0:33:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒那麼弱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.71,0:33:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.86,0:33:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.21,0:34:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.83,0:34:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這次一定會做得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.83,0:35:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,比上次更厲害了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.66,0:35:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.11,0:35:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.23,0:36:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫蕩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.90,0:36:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.83,0:36:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.44,0:37:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.27,0:37:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,多摸一些
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.58,0:38:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.20,0:38:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡好濕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.28,0:38:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要好好地舔這裡
