Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.25,0:41:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.93,0:42:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.98,0:44:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可以插入嗎?
