Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.24,0:45:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,插入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.91,0:45:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要做嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.52,0:45:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.15,0:45:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一定會讓妳爽的
