Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.41,0:47:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,超級爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.55,0:47:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.80,0:47:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我再舔一次可以嗎?
