Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.03,1:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,已經挺不起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.74,1:09:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我來讓你爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.08,1:09:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
